is actually a GENGAR running past you, pretending to be your shadow."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Deep in the night, your shadow cast by a streetlight may suddenly overtake you. It is actually a GENGAR running past you, pretending to be your shadow."},{"version":"firered","text":"It is said to emerge from darkness to steal the lives of those who become lost in mountains."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"On the night of a full moon, if shadows move on their own and laugh, it must be GENGAR\u2019s doing."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It hides in shadows. It is said that if GENGAR is hiding, it cools the area by nearly 10 degrees F."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Lurking in the shadowy corners of rooms, it awaits chances to steal its prey\u2019s life force."},{"version":"platinum","text":"The leer that floats in darkness belongs to a GENGAR delighting in casting curses on people."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It steals heat from its surroundings. If you feel a sudden chill, it is certain that a GENGAR appeared."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"To steal the life of its target, it slips into the prey\u2019s shadow and silently waits for an opportunity."},{"version":"black","text":"The leer that floats in darkness belongs to a Gengar delighting in casting curses on people."},{"version":"white","text":"The leer that floats in darkness belongs to a Gengar delighting in casting curses on people."},{"version":"black-2","text":"The leer that floats in darkness belongs to a Gengar delighting in casting curses on people."},{"version":"white-2","text":"The leer that floats in darkness belongs to a Gengar delighting in casting curses on people."},{"version":"x","text":"It hides in shadows. It is said that if Gengar is hiding, it cools the area by nearly 10 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"version":"y","text":"Hiding in people\u2019s shadows at night, it absorbs their heat. The chill it causes makes the victims shake."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Sometimes, on a dark night, your shadow thrown by a streetlight will suddenly and startlingly overtake you. It is actually a Gengar running past you, pretending to be your shadow."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Sometimes, on a dark night, your shadow thrown by a streetlight will suddenly and startlingly overtake you. It is actually a Gengar running past you, pretending to be your shadow."},{"version":"sun","text":"Should you feel yourself attacked by a sudden chill, it is evidence of an approaching Gengar. There is no escaping it. Give up."},{"version":"moon","text":"It apparently wishes for a traveling companion. Since it was once human itself, it tries to create one by taking the lives of other humans."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"You can hear tales told all over the world about how Gengar will pay a visit to children who are naughty."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Even your home isn\u2019t safe. Gengar will lurk in whatever dark corner of a room it can find and wait for its chance to catch its prey."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"A Gengar is close by if you feel a sudden chill. It may be trying to lay a curse on you."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"A Gengar is close by if you feel a sudden chill. It may be trying to lay a curse on you."},{"version":"sword","text":"On the night of a full moon, if shadows move on their own and laugh, it must be Gengar\u2019s doing."},{"version":"shield","text":"It is said to emerge from darkness to steal the lives of those who become lost in mountains."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Possesses potential victims' shadows in an effort to steal away the victims' lives. If your shadow begins to laugh, you must take hold of a protective charm posthaste!"}],"evo":{"name":"gastly","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"e